paragraph.content:
any receptacle or thing whatever containing or enclosing for keeping or
                        storing or for transporting by sea, air or land, in whatever number or size,
                        any containers referred to in paragraph (a) or (b);

for the purpose of obtaining, whether for himself or for any other person,
                    the issue or renewal of a licence or permit, makes any declaration or statement
                    which is false in a material particular; or

subparagraph.content:
the cancellation, revocation and suspension of any such registration;
                            (Amended 64 of 1994 s.
                            14)
